  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Employees working in IT industry are prone to develop musculoskeletal pain,specifically back,
      neck and shoulder pain. This study evaluates the effectiveness of work-site yoga
      intervention, Yoga@work on neck and shoulder pain in IT employees.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
